Just come on …. It’s all right, so they might get a part of it. Just come in front, there. Or you can sit in the middle, doesn’t matter. You can sit there wherever you are, yes, you can. Come forward, come forward, there’s space here. So I was telling them about Shri Ganesha, that His essential power comes through His humility; and that we all have to be extremely humble, extremely humble, appreciating everything. Of course, you must make them hear My lecture – they have already taped it – so they will know what I am saying today. But now we can have the puja. May God bless you.  

